description:
kubalibre.com -- some fixes
version 0.7

[0.1]
-- Moved FooterBar to top;
-- Repainted main menu bar (the red one).

[0.2]
-- Light gray borders on 'userdetails.php' and 'my.php' pages instead of black.

[0.3]
-- removed whitespaces on main search-bar and torrent-list table header.

[0.4]
-- completely rewritten css-code because of new site design;
-- 'palma' and 'logo' images was removed;
-- toolbar has fixed position on top;
-- quick-search-bar was moved on toolbar and set fixed;
-- torrents-search-bar now looks better;
-- torrents-list table header now smaller.

[0.5]
-- changed menu-bar colors from red to blue;
-- menu-bar has reduced height;
-- fixed colors on search-bar.

[0.6]
-- now menu-bar is also fixed on top.

[0.7]
-- added gradient to main-panel and menu-bar;
-- added 'kubalibre' text on the right side of menu-bar.

